title: Looking for a bronze to silver team
body: I main top but can play most roles

replies.body:

My lane prefs are adc>mid>sup>top>jg, but I've made a point of being able to play any lane with at least a few champs. Let me know if you're keen.
Hey I main (Mid) but can play either top,adc,jg
